* [http://www.ahds.ac.uk/linguistic-corpora Developing Linguistic Corpora: a Guide to Good Practice]{{Webarchive|url=https://archive.is/20121222193153/http://www.ahds.ac.uk/linguistic-corpora |date=2012-12-22 }}
